---
title: Smart Honey Garlic Pork with Roasted Veggie Jumble
description: This classic recipe uses some of the finest hearty veggies, but it doesn't stop there! Juicy seared pork chops get dressed with a no-work honey garlic sauce, proving that sometimes simple and reliable is just what you need!

